vim index.html
edited file + save + exit

Now,
git status

There is 1 untracked/modified file


Working Area:
git clean -n -d: dry run (preview)(untracked files and directories, which are going to be deleted from Working Area)
git clean -f -d: forcefully delete the untracked files and directories from Working Area


Before git add
---------------
git restore index.html----->If I would like to discard the changes before git add index.html



After git add
--------------
git restore --staged index.html--------->If I would like to unstage



After git commit
-----------------
git reset --soft HEAD~1: latest commit will be delted, but files are staged.
git reset --hard HEAD~1: everything will be deleted till last commit.



